DATAOVERVIEW

I used the following code to do some cleaning for the statements csv, which I dont actually present in the analysis. (I also did some manipulation by hand in the csv, so things arent complete.) (Also, file names may have changed.)

stats_raw %>%
  rename(per_id = `..per_id`) %>%
  select(-matches("^x$|^x\\.[0-9]+"))

# then, I used write.csv to write this back to "statements_final.csv"
